Title: kernel.performance: New kernel performance check that consolidates kernel checks into one service
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: incomp
Edition: cre
Version: 2.0.0i1
Date: 1567514360
Class: feature

There is a new service named 'Kernel Performance'. The three services for kernel checks of 'Context Switches', 'Major Page Faults' and 'Process Creation' get combined into this one service.
This reduces the service count by two services. The history of performance data for these three services get lost.
